### Get all materials
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials

### Get material by ID
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials/1

### Get materials by type
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials/by-type/Raw

### Create material
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "MAT-001",
  "name": "Cold Rolled Steel",
  "type": "Raw",
  "description": "Used for fastener production",
  "unitOfMeasure": "kg"
}

### Update material
PUT {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "MAT-001",
  "name": "Cold Rolled Steel Updated",
  "type": "Raw",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "unitOfMeasure": "kg"
}

### Deactivate material
DELETE {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials/1